  "_comment": "Dev/functional matrix for a single-vCPU Linode (Ubuntu 24.04). libzmq and monocoque cover all five kinds; zmq.rs covers throughput, latency, and pub/sub. On 1 vCPU the producer and consumer share the core, so these numbers validate the harness mechanics, not engine performance. cpuset.cpus=0 is the only core available.",
